OL,3,E"ARE YOU GOINGG````````````````````````
OL,5,GI would like to see a special story    
OL,6, from The Man over the Christmas        
OL,7, holidays. I am not alone in this need  
OL,8, for more Man stories. Many others also 
OL,9, have this craving for their lovable    
OL,10, bloke, with that Hill-style chin.      
OL,11, Please make our Christmas worthwhile.  
OL,12,BEdward B                               
OL,14,FPage 174 on Saturday will be entirely  
OL,15,Fdedicated to The Man, as will a special
OL,16,Fretro feature on page 171 on New Year's
OL,17,FDay. You might also like to read The   
OL,18,FNativity Play on our Web site. Happy?  
