OL,3,ETO SCARBOROUGH FAIR?G``````````````````
OL,5, Isn't it nice to see the games market  
OL,6, booming again with lots of quality     
OL,7, games being released?                  
OL,9, I was starting to lose hope a few      
OL,10, months back when there were absolutely 
OL,11, no games worth buying. Now, I have a   
OL,12, problem! There are so many new games I 
OL,13, will need an overdraft to buy them all.
OL,14, Well I suppose mummykins could buy them
OL,15, for me.BJ.R.G.Jamesig1d1521@lmu.ac.uk  
OL,17,FPerhaps you could speak to your bank   
OL,18,Fmanager. We're sure he could arrange   
OL,19,Foverdraft or credit facilities.        
