OL,3,EPARSLEY SAGE ROSEMARYG`````````````````
OL,5, What's this new VRX console thingy     
OL,6, that's comming out? I've heard that    
OL,7, it's really powerful, and yet cheap.   
OL,9, Oh, and what's the story with Quake on 
OL,10, the N64? It's a bit late isn't it!     
OL,11, Finally, how much will Zelda: Ocarina  
OL,12, of Time be? I've heard it's a 100Mbit  
OL,13, cart!BM Sealey@hotmail.com             
OL,15,FSurely you mean to ask: "How late will 
OL,16,FZelda: Ocarina Of Time be?" And were   
OL,17,Fyou to do so we would reply: "It will  
OL,18,Fbe released very late in the UK."      
