OL,3,EAND THYME"G````````````````````````````
OL,5, I'm not a thick bloke, but I always    
OL,6, assumed the Pentium 2 was merely a     
OL,7, Pentium with MMX.                      
OL,9, Having seen the shape of it I now      
OL,10, think it could be more. Having given up
OL,11, reading all other magazines for Digi I 
OL,12, have lost a good source of info. Get a 
OL,13, hardware page now!BAndrew Welch        
OL,15,FWe don't do that kind of stuff, man.   
OL,16,FWe're quite happy to admit we're well  
OL,17,Fstupid when it comes to PC hardware and
OL,18,Fthat. We'd probably break things.      
